snippet.title: Pocketman Third D Trailer (DOWNLOAD IN DESCRIPTION)
snippet.description:
Download Pocketman Third D here: https://bynine.itch.io/pocketman-third-d

NOTE: Game has been patched to fix a bug where it ran too fast on some people's machines. Sorry, Vinny!

Commercial for the ill-fated monster tamer Pocketman Third D, painstakingly restored from a VHS tape by expert Jarrod Roberts (@docninj). A truly rare find, as this commercial was only aired for 3 hours and 18 minutes before being taken down for attempts at subliminal messaging.
